# BEFORE WRITING

Verify each finding passes ALL checks:
- [ ] File path exists in repository
- [ ] Line numbers match current file content
- [ ] Original snippet is verbatim copy
- [ ] Replacement compiles in context (imports, types, signatures correct)
- [ ] Finding matches a numbered detection rule
